metadata.description: The WatchCharts Jaeger-LeCoultre Market Index is an indicator of the secondary market performance of Jaeger-LeCoultre watches. It is composed of the top 30 models within the brand, sorted and weighted by transaction value. The index shows the average market price (in USD) of these 30 watches over time, and is rebalanced once per year on January 1.
